6
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:22,620
An environment refers to the physical location where your code runs.

7
00:00:22,620 --> 00:00:26,700
It's a machine installed with software for executing a program.

8
00:00:26,700 --> 00:00:30,690
WordPress needs additional programs to be fully functional.

9
00:00:30,690 --> 00:00:34,050
There are two types of environments you'll come across.

10
00:00:34,200 --> 00:00:37,800
The first type of environment is a production environment.

11
00:00:37,800 --> 00:00:42,690
Typically, WordPress sites are hosted by a company with hundreds of servers.

12
